Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.74,0:00:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.26,0:01:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙选手玛盖特和贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.22,0:01:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,展开了一场激战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.15,0:01:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于屏障覆盖了整个竞技场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.86,0:01:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔遭受高温和缺氧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法发挥正常的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陷入了困境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.96,0:01:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.50,0:02:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔用强大的气破坏了屏障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这堆破铜烂铁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通过起死回生的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,取得了胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.44,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手获胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经过苦战获得胜利的贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.40,0:02:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来的对手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的赛亚人，加贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轮到我出场了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.54,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「不要忘记赛亚人的骄傲！贝吉塔VS第6宇宙赛亚人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.26,0:02:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔把场地破坏得一团糟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下一场比赛都无法进行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸，保持这个势头把所有对手都干掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯，别太得意忘形喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔也是，你之后还有孙君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快给我回观众席去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.01,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕这家伙动不动就生气真是讨厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.47,0:03:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这混蛋说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那么容易发火我看了都嫌热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.01,0:03:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都因为你整个会场才会这么热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.23,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太热了，哪儿凉快哪儿呆着去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不许说冷笑话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,热死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,热死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那活动一下热热身子怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两位大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备就绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擂台已重建完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,效率还真高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为火爆的比赛还要持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有尽可能避免因出界而输掉比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.85,0:04:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样大家也不留遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人，象帕大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空中出界判负的规则怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种东西赶紧作废
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没意见吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以，我无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.95,0:04:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样赛场又变大很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，就开始比赛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.35,0:05:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向两连胜的贝吉塔选手发起挑战的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙队伍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贝选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙清爽的赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和第7宇宙严肃的赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.79,0:05:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟是哪位赛亚人能够获得胜利呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个少年也是赛亚人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.88,0:05:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不由得让我回忆起当初和悟空相遇的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，饮茶大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那家伙没有尾巴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.22,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会和悟空一样把尾巴拔掉了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有可能喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.89,0:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个年轻人浑身散发着正气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能和我们这里的赛亚人有着不同的进化路程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以说是正义的英雄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.95,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的赛亚人以沙达拉行星为据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.87,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受雇每日铲奸除恶，保护世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们这里的赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也在尽心竭力地守护地球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.72,0:06:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那里的赛亚人有工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.06,0:06:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和悟空真是天壤之别啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.23,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是我下一个对手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.77,0:06:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使出全力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老孙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得那个赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也能和你一样变身成超级赛亚人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老孙这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么在意那家伙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人就是赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连架势都和我一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.71,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我上了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.01,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别太得意了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.64,0:08:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已经没体力了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个绝招是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.53,0:08:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道是我的冲天炮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.45,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厉害啊，他在普通状态下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然和我势均力敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样看来很难分出胜负啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来你使出全力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赶紧给我变成超级赛亚人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是你刚才的那个变身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.33,0:09:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，知道了就快点变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.87,0:09:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.29,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.96,0:09:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说你不会变成超级赛亚人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有个请求，贝吉塔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.05,0:09:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请教我变身的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.85,0:09:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了在沙达拉行星等着我的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想要变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给宇宙带来和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.40,0:10:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是在战斗中啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你教我变身的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我太失望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.87,0:10:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然在战斗中向我求教？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙在干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.88,0:10:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁知道呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老孙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这混蛋，这样也算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样也算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.48,0:10:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.88,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会让你倒下的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔那家伙，发生什么事了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会他体内的邪恶之血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又在蠢蠢欲动了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这种实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也敢过来参加比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会忘了杀掉对手就算输的规则了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.21,0:11:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你小子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果投降的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就杀了你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就解决掉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但在比赛结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会把你的家乡沙达拉行星毁得连渣都不剩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的家族和亲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会一个不留地杀掉他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这和沙达拉行星没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是你对沙达拉行星下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我的家人下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.92,0:13:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我饶不了你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.30,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我绝对不会放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔被压制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.98,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在发什么呆啊，贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别忘记这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.77,0:15:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愤怒是变成超级赛亚人的契机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别忘了刚才的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再变一次试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变成超级赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫你变你就变！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别让我再重复！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你悟性还真高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔先生是为了教我变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.06,0:16:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才故意对我说一些过分的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.98,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛，原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从一开始就相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说谎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饮茶大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是在训练他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蓝色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是最新的超级赛亚人蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果继续修炼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.33,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也有可能达到这个境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也…有这个实力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.80,0:17:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不要忘了这种疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贝选手，加贝选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彻底昏过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加贝选手，被K.O了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔选手获胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.95,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干得漂亮，贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔先生获得三连胜，干得真漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.58,0:17:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样我们队的形势一片大好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.25,0:18:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕大人，您的血压越来越高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝…贝吉塔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在战斗当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.44,0:18:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向身为对手的我低下了头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.40,0:18:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就等同于你认输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我饶不了这样的赛亚人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.58,0:18:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不要忘记赛亚人的骄傲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.91,0:18:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人的骄傲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.05,0:18:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！我会变得和贝吉塔先生您一样强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要超越我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.97,0:18:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知…知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是绝对不会让你超过我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沙达拉行星的国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.58,0:19:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和您一样，是个既高傲又强大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有机会让我见见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.64,0:19:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔竟然会指导别人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔也是王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.68,0:19:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到同为赛亚人的同伴会感到怀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也会想去锻炼他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论从身体上还是从精神上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起赛亚人的话明明还有我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得他会喜欢你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我并不讨厌贝吉塔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让他感到不爽的，就是你这点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪一点啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将要和获胜的贝吉塔选手对战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后一位第6宇宙选手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希特选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.47,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我方的最后一名选手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.64,0:20:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,压轴的是希特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就没必要着急了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.31,0:20:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他可是我们宇宙活着的传奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.07,0:20:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀手希特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.53,0:20:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来他还真的答应为我们出战啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的，条件是如果获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就将用于移动的立方体交给他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么！把那个立方体？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.29,0:20:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.33,0:20:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个是神的交通工具啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.04,0:20:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果他拿到那个立方体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.05,0:20:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不就可以去其他的宇宙甚至任何地方了吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说尽好话让希特出场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.43,0:20:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是象帕大人您说的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是这样说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但他是一个无论如何都逮不到的杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不是开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那要我去回绝他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.11,0:21:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，事到如今已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.41,0:21:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样也就等于我们的胜利是板上钉钉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.95,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.79,0:21:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不太简单　不见得有答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.00,0:21:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何挣扎　也没有终点站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.25,0:22:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勇敢面对变本加厉的恐怖和危机　并享受一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.63,0:22:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.26,0:22:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想结束我们没完　还想拼到地老天荒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.52,0:22:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还想努力亲手实现　当天梦见的景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.85,0:22:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.36,0:22:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管说我贪心也好　渐渐讨厌我也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.61,0:22:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再怎么取笑我也好　完全没放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.87,0:22:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wow
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.66,0:22:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！我是悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.41,0:22:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于能见识一下那家伙的身手了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.58,0:22:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙绝对不好对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.54,0:22:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会看错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.50,0:22:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.67,0:22:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才的招式，我没看清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.79,0:22:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不仅是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.84,0:22:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连贝吉塔和比克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.25,0:22:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都摸不清他的套路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.46,0:22:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下集 「龙珠超」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.59,0:23:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「第6宇宙最强的战士！杀手希特登场！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.76,0:23:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要看啊

